-- REUTERS SUMMIT-Morgan Stanley hires Mitchell for tailored loans
-- By Lauren Tara LaCapra
-- Mon Jun 16, 2014 06:25PM EDT
-- None



NEW YORK, June 16 (Reuters) - Morgan Stanley <MS.N> has hired Marcus Mitchell from Deutsche Bank AG <DBKGn.DE> to head its tailored lending operation, Morgan Stanley's head of wealth management, Gregory Fleming, said at the Reuters Global Wealth Management on Monday.

Mitchell had overseen loan and deposit products at Deutsche Bank's wealth management arm in the Americas. A Deutsche Bank spokeswoman declined to comment.